<area shape="rect" id="node6" title="dsgrid.dimension.dimension_filters.SupplementalDimensionFilterColumnOperatorModel

Filters base dimension records that have a valid mapping to a supplemental dimension.

Attributes:
 &#160;&#160;&#160;column (str): Column of dimension records to use. Default is &#39;id&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;value (Any): Value to filter on. Default is &#39;%&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;operator (str): Method on pyspark.sql.functions.col to invoke. Default is &#39;like&#39;.
 &#160;&#160;&#160;negate (bool): Filter out valid mappings to this supplemental dimension. Default is False.
" alt="" coords="3583,348,4428,368"/>
